    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1755570/extras/413b991790da857e29f97dd54aa419d1.avif?t=1676042970\" width=600 height=100 /></span><br><br>Kittens are really cute and fun pets, aren't they?<br><br>They have only one function, to be cute! They entertain us with comic moments without much effort, just being themselves.<br><br>With that in mind, we developed this game for those who love kittens and have fun with these unusual scenes that they provide us!<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>A relaxing and fun experience with 20 different levels, 24 fun hand-drawn kitty cards!<br></li><li>Enjoy calm and peaceful music to face the progressive challenges as you level up.<br></li><li>Memory game with puzzles, find the correct path by moving and matching the correct cards!<br></li><li>Release your cards for your collection, this game is for you who love kittens and puzzles!</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1755570/extras/297d57ef0c1f17ad706c26ec49b76fcc.poster.avif?t=1676042970\" width=600 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1755570/extras/297d57ef0c1f17ad706c26ec49b76fcc.webm?t=1676042970\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1755570/extras/297d57ef0c1f17ad706c26ec49b76fcc.mp4?t=1676042970\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
